'''''Tyelca''''' is a [[Quenya]] adjective which means "swift", "agile" or "hasty". 
==Etymology==
Probably [[PQ]] *''kyelekâ'', [[Sundocarmë|Root]] [[KYELEK]]
==Examples==
* [[Tyelkormo]] = Hasty-riser
==Cognates==
*[[Sindarin]] ''[[celeg]]''
